00:00:25.035 --> 00:00:34.710
Holy Spirit, I invite you in this time of prayer. I thank you, Lord, that it is uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:00:34.711 --> 00:00:42.074
Father, I ask you to pray through me. Holy Spirit, I ask you to speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind.

00:00:42.075 --> 00:00:52.799
None of me and all of you, in Jesus'name. Amen. Holy Spirit, we invite Him and we're so thankful for Him.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:57.637
I think the last prayer video was probably one of my favorites of the year so far.

00:00:57.638 --> 00:01:03.929
I don't know how many people watched that, but it truly blessed me.

00:01:03.930 --> 00:01:18.474
Everything the Lord showed me about the revival with John Kilpatrick and the churches around America with Perry Stone—I've just been meditating on it, soaking it in.

00:01:18.475 --> 00:01:29.999
We can go from one place to another and just take for granted what God has done through this channel and what He's showing us so gracefully.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:41.359
Or you can take the moment to pause and just really breathe in that fragrance of who He is and what He's about to do in this earth.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:48.115
It's amazing. I don't want to take for granted those times; they're precious to me.

00:01:48.116 --> 00:02:01.270
Diana and I have been meditating, running those things through our minds and thinking about what God said about Pastor John Kilpatrick.

00:02:01.271 --> 00:02:12.514
I don't even know them or their church, but I've watched some of the online services to catch up with some of the things he's saying.

00:02:12.515 --> 00:02:24.296
They're a hungry church. He had a sermon series in his archives; I listened to two of them and they really blessed me.

00:02:24.297 --> 00:02:45.953
I was trying to think of what it was called, but it was phenomenal. He preaches amazingly. I encourage you all to listen to it.

00:02:45.954 --> 00:02:52.375
We've listened to a bunch of them now because I wanted to know if we're right.

00:02:52.376 --> 00:03:01.511
Whenever you're hearing in the spirit and the Lord's showing you things, you don't want to be flaky.

00:03:01.512 --> 00:03:05.598
I don't want to be a part of the flakiness; I want to flow with the Holy Spirit.

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:15.701
If it's off, it's off. I'm not here to make excuses. If I miss it, I miss it, but I want to be quick to tell you.

00:03:15.702 --> 00:03:29.070
The Lord is telling me that He's going to renew his veins and his arteries, renewing his body like the eagles.

00:03:29.071 --> 00:03:33.148
The glory of the Lord is coming on John Kilpatrick like Moses.

00:03:33.149 --> 00:03:46.530
I saw him sitting in a chair on his platform, and the glory of the Lord was tangible in the atmosphere of the church.

00:03:46.531 --> 00:04:01.279
He was like a big papa bear watching over the flock as the shepherd of that church. The glory of the Lord was tangible.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:11.039
Do you remember I told you mist would show up in services and, as it dissipates, it would leave gold dust on people's skin?

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:25.276
That's what I saw coming even in his church—a mist of the glory where the residue of the glory of the Lord would leave a type of gold dust.

00:04:25.276 --> 00:05:00.369
I know there has been mockery of this, like people trying to fake it, but the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, there's going to be an authentic move of this that won't be mocked, fake, or man-made.'This is going to be a tangible visitation of the Lord that nobody's going to be able to duplicate other than Jesus.

00:05:00.370 --> 00:05:11.219
I saw that at that church and I saw everybody getting healed. I saw the glory of the Lord.

00:05:11.220 --> 00:05:29.817
I know he's probably getting older, but the Lord said, 'I'm about to give him a second wind, a new wind of my glory, a new wind of my presence upon his church.'What happened at Pensacola and the Brownsville Revival will be times ten.

00:05:29.817 --> 00:05:53.458
I thought that was a very interesting number when the Lord said that to me because usually, the Lord deals in double for the trouble or sevenfold or a hundredfold.

00:05:53.459 --> 00:06:15.999
He said times ten. The weightiness of the Brownsville Revival would be times ten in what's about to happen at the Church of His Presence there in Daphne, Alabama.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:23.996
All glory to Jesus; I'm excited for that congregation. Then He showed me Perry Stone.

00:06:23.997 --> 00:06:52.557
In the vision, the Lord showed me John Kilpatrick by himself, but Perry had someone standing beside him, a younger person helping him.

00:06:52.558 --> 00:07:12.758
This would be around the clock, 24 hours a day. I'm talking about glorious church services that you just don't want to unhook from.

00:07:12.759 --> 00:07:25.870
Brother Hagin used to say all the time that sometimes you just have to unhook from a service.

00:07:25.871 --> 00:07:38.271
But what I saw coming were services that you just don't unhook from until you feel it lift.

00:07:38.272 --> 00:07:48.883
God's about to show up and show off in people's lives. I saw massive silos again.

00:07:48.884 --> 00:08:12.878
When I went to heaven before, the Lord allowed me to see the silos with the body parts—eyes, ears, people that needed creative miracles.

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:18.128
Those silos were full of parts, and the Lord said, 'I'm emptying my silos, Brandon.

00:08:18.129 --> 00:08:47.759
There's no need for them up here for what I'm about to do.'This will be the greatest grace explosion, for it's the goodness of God that brings man to repentance.

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:55.419
Goodness and mercy are about to show up and show off in your life.

00:08:55.420 --> 00:09:15.417
I saw waves, and these waves were full of body parts—whatever you needed: kidneys, hearts, lungs, a spleen, a pancreas, or livers.

00:09:15.418 --> 00:09:19.039
I don't want to call them body parts. A body part is not an organ.

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:28.194
I guess a body part is like a finger, or hand, or whatever, but these were organs—like what you need to sustain life, what you have to have.

00:09:28.195 --> 00:09:38.824
They were inside of these waves. And as the wave would crash into the church, into the revival, there was another wave.

00:09:38.825 --> 00:09:54.348
You know how sometimes when you see a massive wave on the beach, it takes a little bit of time for the wave to come back? These waves were right upon each other.

00:09:54.349 --> 00:10:11.476
That's why he started saying, 'The glory, the glory, the glory.'Every time I said 'the glory,'those were waves crashing in and bringing the supply, bringing whatever you needed.

00:10:11.477 --> 00:10:20.125
