00:10:34.850 --> 00:10:42.969
They just believe it. There's no doubt; doubt is taught. The Lord said it's because of mistrust.

00:10:42.970 --> 00:10:49.865
You might disappoint them, and they have a seed of mistrust because of you not fulfilling what you said.

00:10:49.866 --> 00:10:58.989
But God is a God that doesn't come up short. His hand is always full and ready to give unto his children.

00:10:58.990 --> 00:11:11.187
The Lord said, 'Come to me as little children.'I saw the wave of God's glory and I saw great finances.

00:11:11.188 --> 00:11:18.217
And he said, 'Do you see that money?'I said, 'Yeah, I can see it.'But a lot of times when he's talking, I don't tell everything.

00:11:18.218 --> 00:11:23.317
I'm here and I'm seeing—it's all so real. Everything is what the Lord is showing me.

00:11:23.317 --> 00:11:29.172
I saw gold coins. I saw things that the Lord showed me. Brandon, this is the outpouring of finances.

00:11:29.173 --> 00:11:42.799
As I prayed tonight, we were seeing the glory and the tangible presence of the Lord in these services. It was for the youth; it was for the people.

00:11:42.800 --> 00:12:07.850
He said, 'I told you there has to be a foundation of wealth, a wealth transfer.'People go, 'I don't like talking about it because I'm going to talk more about the blood of Jesus, I'm going to talk more about the healing power of God.'But there's a part of it because there's been such a bad taste in a lot of the body of Christ, especially in the charismatic circles, about finances because of things a lot of preachers focused on in the past.

