00:14:18.959 --> 00:14:32.479
It's taught.'If you've never been around money before and your family's always been dead broke and you go from paycheck to paycheck, you don't ask financial advice from people who barely make it financially.

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:41.883
That's stupid. You look at people who have billions in the bank and you go, 'How'd they get it? Is it all legal?'I don't know; it's not my place to judge.

00:14:41.884 --> 00:15:01.759
